<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <style>
      body {
        background-image: url("assets/bg3.png");
        background: cover;
      }
    </style>

    <!-- glass -->
    <section>
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center h-screen">
        <div
          class="bg-[rgba(255,255,255,.65)] rounded-lg backdrop-blur-[10px] border-2 border-gray-300 h-[92%] w-[95%] shadow-xl"
        >
          <div>

            <%- include('partials/navbar.ejs') %>

            <!-- content -->

            <section>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap h-auto justify-center mx-5 mt-5">
                <div class="w-1/2 text-left h-3/5">
                  <div class="w-full object-contain sm:px-0 md:px-10">
                    <h1
                      class="md:text-5xl text-4xl text-[15303B] mt-5 font-bold font-sans"
                    >
                      What is INSAT-3DR ?
                    </h1>
                    <h1 class="text-4xl text-[15303B] font-bold font-sans"></h1>
                    <h1 class="text-4xl text-[15303B] font-bold font-sans"></h1>

                    <h4 class="mt-10 text-xl">
                      INSAT-3DR similar to INSAT-3D, is an advanced
                      meteorological satellite of India configured with an
                      imaging System and an Atmospheric Sounder. The significant
                      improvements incorporated in INSAT-3DR are:-
                    </h4>

                    <ul class="px-7 mt-5 text-base list-disc">
                      <li>
                        Imaging in Middle Infrared band to provide night time
                        pictures of low clouds and fog.
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        Imaging in two Thermal Infrared bands for estimation of
                        Sea Surface Temperature (SST) with better accuracy.
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        Higher Spatial Resolution in the Visible and Thermal
                        Infrared bands.
                        <a
                          href="https://www.isro.gov.in/Spacecraft/insat-3dr"
                          class="underline font-semibold hover:text-indigo-400 hover:animate-pulse text-lg"
                          >Know more</a
                        >
                      </li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div
                  class="flex relative justify-start items-center h-full w-1/2"
                >
                  <div class="flex justify-center items-center p-10">
                    <img
                      class="h-[25rem] px-2 inset-0 blur-xl absolute"
                      src="assets/info.png"
                      alt=""
                    />
                    <img
                      class="h-[25rem] inset-0 px-2 absolute"
                      src="assets/insat.png"
                      alt=""
                    />
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </section>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </body>
</html>
